OL,3,CUse heat pumps over gas boilers for
OL,4,CBritish-made energy, say researchers
OL,6,FPeople who want to use more British-
OL,7,Fmade energy for their central heating
OL,8,Fshould use a heat pump rather than a
OL,9,Ftraditional boiler, according to
OL,10,Fresearch.
OL,12,FHouseholds using heat pumps use only
OL,13,Fhalf the imported energy as those with
OL,14,Fgas boilers, said the Energy and
OL,15,FClimate Intelligence Unit (ECIU) think
OL,16,Ftank.
