OL,3,CUse heat pumps over gas boilers for
OL,4,CBritish-made energy, say researchers
OL,6,FHeat pumps run on electricity, a
OL,7,Fhigher proportion of which is
OL,8,Fgenerated using homegrown energy
OL,9,Fsources like wind turbines and solar
OL,10,Fpanels.
OL,12,FBy contrast, much of the UK's gas
OL,13,Fsupply is imported from countries like
OL,14,FNorway and the United States.
OL,16,FInternational gas prices have spiked
OL,17,Fin recent years due to Russia's
OL,18,Finvasion of Ukraine, pushing up
OL,19,Fhousehold energy bills.
