OL,3,CUse heat pumps over gas boilers for
OL,4,CBritish-made energy, say researchers
OL,6,FThe ECIU said a household with a heat
OL,7,Fpump will use 2.9 megawatt hours
OL,8,Fcompared to 5.7 megawatt hours per
OL,9,Fyear with a gas boiler for a home with
OL,10,Fan EPC rating of C.
OL,12,FJess Ralston, energy analyst at the
OL,13,FECIU, said the heat pump rollout would
OL,14,Fhelp the UK "wean itself of foreign
OL,15,Fenergy imports, boosting the UK's
OL,16,Fenergy security as British renewables
OL,17,Framp up rapidly".
