OL,3,CUse heat pumps over gas boilers for
OL,4,CBritish-made energy, say researchers
OL,6,FShe added: "We know that continuing to
OL,7,Frely on gas boilers just means we'll
OL,8,Fsee our imports rise, so any boiler
OL,9,Fmanufacturers that stand in the way of
OL,10,Fprogress on heat pumps are lobbying
OL,11,Ffor higher foreign gas imports and
OL,12,Fless energy security."
OL,14,FHeat pumps are much more expensive to
OL,15,Fbuy and install than gas boilers but
OL,16,Fthey are also more energy efficient,
OL,17,Fmeaning they use less power to heat
OL,18,Fhomes.
