OL,3,CUse heat pumps over gas boilers for
OL,4,CBritish-made energy, say researchers
OL,6,FThe Government wants them to be rolled
OL,7,Fout at scale to help cut carbon
OL,8,Femissions from building heating.
OL,10,FEarlier in November, ministers put #30
OL,11,Fmillion more into a grant scheme which
OL,12,Fgives households #7,500 off the cost
OL,13,Fof buying a heat pump.
OL,15,FLabour also promised to change
OL,16,Fplanning rules that require heat pumps
OL,17,Fto be at least one metre from the
OL,18,Fproperty boundary, to help encourage
OL,19,Ftake-up.
