OL,3,CUse heat pumps over gas boilers for
OL,4,CBritish-made energy, say researchers
OL,6,FOfficials say heat pumps used
OL,7,Feffectively with a smart "time of use"
OL,8,Felectricity tariff could save around
OL,9,F#100 a year compared to a gas boiler,
OL,10,Fwhile better insulation could cut
OL,11,Fbills by around #200 a year.
OL,13,FThe ECIU added that if a recent push
OL,14,Fto build more renewable energy sources
OL,15,Flike wind and solar farms continues,
OL,16,Fthe amount of imported power a heat
OL,17,Fpump uses could halve again by 2030.
