OL,3,CUse heat pumps over gas boilers for
OL,4,CBritish-made energy, say researchers
OL,6,FThat would mean the devices use as
OL,7,Flittle as a sixth of the imported
OL,8,Fenergy that gas boilers use by the end
OL,9,Fof the decade.
OL,11,FThe Government also announced a
OL,12,F"reformed" clean heat market mechanism
OL,13,F` delayed by the previous government `
OL,14,Ffor April 2025, requiring 6% of sales
OL,15,Fby boiler manufacturers to be heat
OL,16,Fpumps or for them to pay a charge for
OL,17,Feach missed installation.
