OL,6,FIt said the new version of the scheme,
OL,7,Fwith the charge reduced from #3,000 to
OL,8,F#500 for the first year with
OL,9,Fconsultation on further years, would
OL,10,Fgive manufacturers ` who pushed back
OL,11,Fagainst what they called the "boiler
OL,12,Ftax" ` the time they need to scale up
OL,13,Fsupply chains.
OL,15,FAnd there would be Government support
OL,16,Ffor every heat pump installation that
OL,17,Fis required under the mechanism in
OL,18,F2025/2026, officials added.
